column2: SELECT TOP # so.ra,so.dec,so.z,so.z_noqso,so.class,so.subclass, so.class_noqso, so.subclass_noqso, so.survey,so.programname,so.primtarget,so.sourcetype, po.objid,po.ra,po.dec,po.u,po.g,po.r,po.i,po.z, po.run, po.rerun, po.camcol, po.field,po.type, po.psfmag_u-po.extinction_u AS mag_u, po.psfmag_g-po.extinction_g AS mag_g, po.psfmag_r-po.extinction_r AS mag_r, po.psfmag_i-po.extinction_i AS mag_i, po.psfmag_z-po.extinction_z AS mag_z, w.w1mpro AS w1, w.w2mpro AS w2, w.w3mpro AS w3, w.w4mpro AS w4 FROM PhotoObj AS po LEFT JOIN SpecObj AS so ON so.bestobjid = po.objid JOIN wise_xmatch AS xm ON so.bestobjid = xm.sdss_objid JOIN wise_allsky AS w ON xm.wise_cntr = w.cntr JOIN PhotoZ as pz ON pz.objid = po.objid WHERE  so.bestobjid IS NULL
